# OS / editor junk only.
# IMPORTANT: Do NOT ignore your data here.
# The live site on GitHub Pages can only serve data that is committed to git:
#   - assets/girls.xml            (list of girls)
#   - assets/responses.xml        (all responses - your most important data)
#   - assets/<girl>/profile.xml   (each girl's page data)
#   - assets/<girl>/responses.xml (each girl's backup responses)
#   - assets/<girl>/*.jpg|*.png   (each girl's photos)
# These MUST stay tracked. Use Admin -> "Backup & restore" to keep safe copies.

